review_res.text: I first compare the fruit on the left to all of the subsequent fruits until it is less than one of them in weight. Them I start with that one and compare to all subsequent, until one of them is clearly the heaviest. Once I've identified that, I try to compare middle-weight fruits to determine the correct order of them. If I sense a pattern, I don't necessarily weigh/compare all, in the interest of moving quickly.

review_res.text: I compared the heaviest in one box with the heaviest from another, since they're already partially sorted.
